hopobject.body: real beauty page antibiotico.com.es Madonna struck a provocative pose in an advertisement for luxury designer Louis Vuitton. Considering the singer's controversial past photographic exploits ('Erotica' anyone?), the ad is hardly shocking, but the material girl sure seems to know how to showcase a hand bag. Madonna was personally picked by designer Marc Jacobs to headline the campaign, hitting newsstands near you.
